1. *Bile* su vrele i svi smo se znojili. (They were hot and we were all sweating.)
2. On se smejao *bile* su mu oči sjale. (He was laughing and his eyes were shining.)
3. *Bile* su boje njene oči najljepše na svetu. (Her eyes were the most beautiful in the world.)
4. *Bile* su njegove ruke meke i tople. (His hands were soft and warm.)
5. Mi smo se smejali dok su *bile* njegove šale smešne. (We were laughing while his jokes were funny.)